他在商场上以强硬着称

175
00:10:48,49 --> 00:10:51,93
Ladies and gentlemen,introducing...
各位先生、女士，让我们欢迎

176
00:10:52,16 --> 00:10:54,65
... Pete Becker!
彼特贝克

177
00:11:00,34 --> 00:11:01,74
I love you,Pete!
彼特，我爱你

178
00:11:05,84 --> 00:11:09,87
And his opponent, from Huntington Beach,California...
他的对手来自加州亨丁顿滩

179
00:11:10,08 --> 00:11:13,85
... he's a 300-pound streetfighter...
重达300磅的街头搏击好手

180
00:11:14,35 --> 00:11:16,75
...Tank Abbott!
坦克艾博特

181
00:11:29,63 --> 00:11:30,43
Pete?
彼特

182
00:11:30,70 --> 00:11:31,53
Pete?
彼特

183
00:11:31,94 --> 00:11:34,13
-That guy's pretty huge. -Don't worry.
那砘锖每梧 你放心

184
00:11:34,41 --> 00:11:36,87
I'll use his strength and weight against him.
我会用他的力量反击他

185
00:11:37,14 --> 00:11:41,37
Well,then that guy is in serious, serious trouble.
那他的麻烦大了

186
00:11:46,48 --> 00:11:48,28
You go get him. Let's go!
打倒他，加油

187
00:11:49,62 --> 00:11:51,28
Here we go,gentlemen.
两位，来吧

188
00:11:51,56 --> 00:11:52,82
Are you ready?
准备好了吗？

189
00:11:55,99 --> 00:11:58,55
Are you ready? Then let's get it on!
准备好了吗？开战吧

190
00:12:20,82 --> 00:12:22,01
It's me.
是我

191
00:12:22,92 --> 00:12:24,62
Monica.
摩妮卡

192
00:12:27,43 --> 00:12:30,02
Can I just tell you how proud I am of you?
我真的很以你为荣

193
00:12:30,23 --> 00:12:34,19
It would be nice after hearing 20,000 people chant,"You suck!"
真窝心，刚才有两万人骂我逊

194
00:12:35,47 --> 00:12:37,46
I thought you were nuts at first...
我原本觉得你疯了

195
00:12:37,70 --> 00:12:39,26
... but you did it.
但是你做到了

196
00:12:39,67 --> 00:12:42,66
Now you can just look back at this with no regrets.
现在你可以了无遗撼了

197
00:12:42,87 --> 00:12:44,34
Look back?
了无遗撼？

198
00:12:45,14 --> 00:12:47,01
You're not gonna keep going?
你不是还要打吧？

199
00:12:47,38 --> 00:12:51,08
Let me ask you a question: Am I the Ultimate Fighting Champion?
我问你一件事 我是终极格斗冠军吗？

200
00:12:53,22 --> 00:12:54,88
Well,no. But
不是，但是…

201
00:12:55,19 --> 00:12:58,42
I'm not gonna stop until I'm the Ultimate Fighting Champion.
不当上冠军，我绝不罢休

202
00:12:59,52 --> 00:13:03,32
That guy stood on your neck until you passed out.
那砘锊茸拍愕牟弊 把你踩昏

203
00:13:04,13 --> 00:13:05,82
Let me tell you a story.
我告诉你一个故事

204
00:13:06,73 --> 00:13:11,03
When I set out to create MOSS 865, do you think it happened overnight?
我着手研发的摩斯865 你以为是一夕成功？

205
00:13:11,30 --> 00:13:15,71
No. There was MOSS 1 that burned down my dad's garage.
不是，摩斯一代 烧毁我爸的车库

206
00:13:15,97 --> 00:13:19,88
There was MOSS 2 that would only schedule appointments in January.
摩斯二代只能排一月的行程表

207
00:13:20,08 --> 00:13:22,48
And 862 others that I learned from.
此外还有862次的失败经验

208
00:13:22,68 --> 00:13:26,48
Just like I learned from this fight, never to let a guy stand on my neck.
我从这场比赛就学到 绝不能让对手踩我的脖子

209
00:13:26,68 --> 00:13:28,91
You didn't know that already?
你之前不知道？

210
00:13:30,42 --> 00:13:32,41
Look,I'm gonna get better.
我会越来越强

211
00:13:33,26 --> 00:13:35,35
Okay? I promise you.
好吗？我保证

212
00:13:39,10 --> 00:13:41,43
Just get a lot better.
要强很多

213
00:13:41,87 --> 00:13:43,27
Fast.
而且要快

214
00:13:45,44 --> 00:13:46,49
One other thing.
还有一件事

215
00:13:46,74 --> 00:13:50,40
Hoshi thinks you being ringside may have affected my concentration.
星认为你在场边 会影响我的注意力

216
00:13:52,74 --> 00:13:54,51
That was the problem.
对，关键就在这里

217
00:14:01,09 --> 00:14:03,95
-How long until Pete's fight? -About five minutes.
彼特的比赛几点开始？ 还有五分钟

218
00:14:04,22 --> 00:14:05,88
They're interviewing his opponent.
他们在访问他的对手

219
00:14:06,12 --> 00:14:10,22
Apparently,he trains by going to lran and pulling the arms off thieves.
他的训练方式是 去伊朗拔断小偷的手臂

220
00:14:11,60 --> 00:14:13,76
-Hot dog? -Four,please.
热狗？ 四根

221
00:14:14,37 --> 00:14:15,96
I'm really nervous.
我很紧张

222
00:14:16,90 --> 00:14:17,96
Thank you.
谢谢

223
00:14:20,24 --> 00:14:23,37
So how did it go with Bonnie?
你跟邦妮怎么样？

224
00:14:23,61 --> 00:14:27,81
Oh,I gotta tell you, I wasn't expecting to like her at all.
我一定要说 我没想到我会喜欢她

225
00:14:28,08 --> 00:14:30,98
I actually wasn't expecting to like anyone right now.
我目前根本没打算要喜欢别人

226
00:14:31,25 --> 00:14:33,27
But she's really terrific.
但她真的很棒

227
00:14:33,55 --> 00:14:34,45
It's too bad.
真糟糕

228
00:14:36,92 --> 00:14:39,32
No,I'm saying I liked her.
我是说我喜欢她

229
00:14:39,59 --> 00:14:41,49
There are other fish in the sea.
你不必单恋一枝花

230
00:14:42,76 --> 00:14:45,99
I think she's great,okay? We're going out again.
我觉得她很棒，我们要再见面

231
00:14:46,63 --> 00:14:49,76
I hear you. Are you capable of talking about anything else?
我听到了 你可以谈点别的吗？

232
00:14:51,67 --> 00:14:53,66
Which one's my turkey burger?
我的土鸡汉堡在哪里？

233
00:14:53,97 --> 00:14:56,17
The one next to my foot. Sorry.
在我脚边…抱歉

234
00:14:57,17 --> 00:14:59,40
-Fight's starting! -We'll be right in.
比赛开始了 马上进去

235
00:14:59,61 --> 00:15:02,48
So did your boss try to slap you again today?
你的上司今天又打你了吗？

236
00:15:02,68 --> 00:15:04,15
Nine times.
九次

237
00:15:04,98 --> 00:15:06,57
I had to put on lotion.
害我得擦润肤乳液

238
00:15:08,82 --> 00:15:11,69
But it'll be okay. Tomorrow,I conduct an experiment.
不过没关系 我明天要做个实验

239
00:15:11,96 --> 00:15:15,92
And if all goes as planned, my butt will be smack-free.
要是顺利，我的屁股就得救了

240
00:15:16,59 --> 00:15:17,79
Fight's over!
比赛结束

241
00:15:23,40 --> 00:15:24,80
Excuse me,Doug?
道格？

242
00:15:27,27 --> 00:15:29,26
Hey there,sports fan!
超级运动迷！

243
00:15:29,64 --> 00:15:32,11
Bing! You got those numbers for me?
宾，数据做好了吗？

244
00:15:32,31 --> 00:15:34,24
No. I didn't do them.
没有，我没做

245
00:15:34,51 --> 00:15:36,34
You forgot?
你忘了？

246
00:15:36,65 --> 00:15:39,01
No,I just didn't do them.
不是，我就是没做

247
00:15:39,32 --> 00:15:43,01
Instead,I hung out with some friends and had a couple of beers.
我跟朋友出去，喝了两杯

248
00:15:43,29 --> 00:15:45,95
So I certainly don't deserve praise. Verbal...
所以我不值得表扬 不管是言语上…

249
00:15:46,19 --> 00:15:47,78
...or otherwise.
或其他方式

250
00:15:48,43 --> 00:15:51,52
I got tanked myself last night. Pretty dicey drive home.
我昨晚也醉了 是某个美眉载我回家的

251
00:15:51,76 --> 00:15:54,20
Tappan Zee Bridge never looked smaller.
塔本吉桥变得好小

252
00:15:55,27 --> 00:15:58,43
That's okay. You're still my number-one guy! Bing!
没关系，你还是我的 头号爱将，宾！

253
00:15:59,04 --> 00:16:00,63
Doug!
道格

254
00:16:01,51 --> 00:16:06,00
I'm a little bit uncomfortable with the way that you express yourself.
我对你的表达方式有点不习惯

255
00:16:06,21 --> 00:16:08,77
Is it the swearing? Is it the constant swearing?
你是说我经常骂脏话？

256
00:16:08,98 --> 00:16:12,97
Because I gotta tell you,if it is, you can just kiss my ass!
如果是的话 你可以亲我的屁股

257
00:16:15,05 --> 00:16:17,78
It's not about the swearing. It's more about...
不是骂脏话的事，而是…

258
00:16:18,02 --> 00:16:20,51
...the way that you occasionally...
你偶尔会…

259
00:16:20,79 --> 00:16:24,23
...concentrate your enthusiasm...
把注意力集中在…

260
00:16:25,50 --> 00:16:27,02
...on my buttocks.
我的屁股上

261
00:16:29,50 --> 00:16:32,40
Don't get me wrong. I appreciate the sentiment.
别误会，我了解你的用意

262
00:16:32,64 --> 00:16:36,40
It's just that I have a rather sensitive posterior.
只不过我的臀部很敏感

263
00:16:38,31 --> 00:16:41,61
And besides,it's making all the other guys jealous.
而且别人都在嫉妒

264
00:16:41,81 --> 00:16:45,75
Well,say no more. You know, it takes guts to bring this up.
别再说了，你确实很有勇气

265
00:16:46,05 --> 00:16:48,02
Bing,you're okay.
宾，很好

266
00:16:58,33 --> 00:17:01,86
Would you rather live in the shirt pocket of a sweaty giant...
你要住在满身大汗的 巨人的上衣口袋

267
00:17:02,10 --> 00:17:04,59
...or inside his shower drain?
还是他的排水管里？

268
00:17:06,67 --> 00:17:07,86
Oh,my God.
天哪

269
00:17:08,44 --> 00:17:10,50
Look. It's Ross and that girl.
你看，是罗斯和那个女的

270
00:17:13,84 --> 00:17:18,34
Look at that! It's a line of ants! They're working as a team!
你看，有一排蚂蚁 他们在同心协力

271
00:17:20,35 --> 00:17:24,45
Right. Oh,yeah. It looks like Ross is breaking up with her.
他们啊 罗斯好像要跟她分手了

272
00:17:24,72 --> 00:17:26,19
I hope he lets her down easy.
希望他不要太狠

273
00:17:26,42 --> 00:17:29,42
Look at that! They are not breaking up! Look at them!
你看，他们没有要分手

274
00:17:29,63 --> 00:17:32,69
You know what that is? A second date,that's what that is.
那只是第二次的约会

275
00:17:33,30 --> 00:17:35,60
Look,she just put her hand on his thigh.
你看，她把手放到他的大腿上

276
00:17:35,80 --> 00:17:38,43
That's nothing. She's very sexually aggressive.
小意思，她在性方面很主动

277
00:17:38,70 --> 00:17:39,73
Oh,God!
天哪

278
00:17:40,04 --> 00:17:44,77
It's your fault. Now he loves her. He'll marry her. It's all your fault.
都是你不好，他爱上她了 他会娶她，都是你的错

279
00:17:45,48 --> 00:17:46,97
You said it was okay.
你自己说没关系

280
00:17:47,28 --> 00:17:49,34
You said she was bald!
你说她是光头

281
00:17:50,81 --> 00:17:53,15
Was! Was,was,was!
以前！以前…

282
00:17:54,45 --> 00:17:58,44
We can't let it happen. We have to do something. We have to break them up.
我们得想个办法 我们得拆散他们

283
00:17:58,76 --> 00:18:02,95
Just go in there and shave her head! You owe me one bald girl!
进去帮她剃光头 你欠我一个光头女

284
00:18:04,80 --> 00:18:06,56
Okay,first of all,breathe.
你先深呼吸

285
00:18:07,80 --> 00:18:10,23
Second of all,I don't get it.
再来，我实在不懂

286
00:18:10,50 --> 00:18:13,60
Aren't you the one that decided you didn't want to be with Ross?
不是你决定要跟罗斯分手的？

287
00:18:17,07 --> 00:18:20,77
Well,isn't he your friend? Don't you want him to be happy?
他不是你的朋友吗？ 你不希望他快乐吗？

288
00:18:24,98 --> 00:18:26,14
So?
所以？

289
00:18:30,42 --> 00:18:34,91
It's just,you know,I didn't expect him to be this happy so soon.
但是我没想到会这么快

290
00:18:44,70 --> 00:18:45,67
-Oh,no. -What?
完了 怎样？

291
00:18:45,87 --> 00:18:46,96
We killed them all!
它们被我们坐死了

292
00:19:03,19 --> 00:19:06,05
It's not as bad as it looks. It's a precaution.
没这么严重，这是以防万一

293
00:19:06,32 --> 00:19:08,81
I'm not supposed to move my spine.
我的脊椎骨不能动

294
00:19:11,36 --> 00:19:13,19
Please tell me you're stopping now.
你要放弃了吧？

295
00:19:13,63 --> 00:19:16,33
I'm fine. I'd fight tonight if they'd let me.
我没事，今晚要我上场都行

296
00:19:18,04 --> 00:19:20,63
Now,see this circle I'm marking off here?
你看这个圆

297
00:19:20,87 --> 00:19:22,84
This is my Zone of Terror.
这是我的“恐怖区”

298
00:19:25,58 --> 00:19:28,98
You are insane! You've got to give this up!
你疯了，你一定要放弃

299
00:19:29,18 --> 00:19:32,08
I can't until I'm the Ultimate Fighter.
除非我拿到格斗冠军

300
00:19:32,32 --> 00:19:33,51
I will do it.
我会成功的

301
00:19:33,72 --> 00:19:37,98
The day will come when children will argue over who will win a fight...
总有一天 小朋友会争辩我和超人…

302
00:19:38,22 --> 00:19:40,16
...me or Superman.
谁会打赢

303
00:19:41,99 --> 00:19:45,05
Not that I could beat Superman, but kids are stupid.
我赢不过超人 不过小孩子都很笨

304
00:19:46,26 --> 00:19:47,53
Just sit down.
你先坐下

305
00:19:47,73 --> 00:19:49,60
Please listen to me.
听我说

306
00:19:49,83 --> 00:19:54,83
You are terrible at this,okay? You are the worst Ultimate Fighter ever.
你打得很烂，你是史上 最烂的终极格斗手

307
00:19:55,34 --> 00:19:56,27
Ever!
最烂的

308
00:19:57,71 --> 00:20:01,77
I have a torn rotator cuff,a hairline fracture in my right forearm...
我的肌腱套破裂 右前臂有轻微骨折

309
00:20:02,01 --> 00:20:06,11
...and a severely bruised Adam's apple,but that really hurt.
喉结严重瘀伤 但你的话最伤人

310
00:20:11,76 --> 00:20:14,02
Well,then,you know what?
那么你知道吗？

311
00:20:16,09 --> 00:20:20,26
I care about you too much to watch you hurt yourself like this.
我没办法看你这样伤害自己

312
00:20:20,73 --> 00:20:24,13
So if you have to do this, you'll have to do it without me.
要是你非打不可 我就不奉陪了

313
00:20:24,64 --> 00:20:26,57
If you're asking me to quit...
如果你要我放弃

314
00:20:26,87 --> 00:20:29,63
...then you're asking me to be someone I'm not.
就是要我违背本性

315
00:20:29,94 --> 00:20:31,41
I've got to do this.
我非打不可

316
00:20:35,75 --> 00:20:37,58
Then I've gotta go.
那我要走了

317
00:20:39,45 --> 00:20:40,42
Bye.
再见

318
00:20:48,73 --> 00:20:50,82
Could you leave a note? I'm on painkillers...
你可以留张字条吗？ 我服了止痛药

319
00:20:51,09 --> 00:20:53,22
...and I might not remember this tomorrow.
明天可能会忘记这件事

320
00:20:58,67 --> 00:21:03,66
So,in conclusion,the lines all go up,so I'm happy.
总而言之，曲线节节上升 我很满意

321
00:21:04,57 --> 00:21:06,91
Great job,team! Tomorrow at 8:30.
干得好，明天八点半见

322
00:21:07,51 --> 00:21:10,57
Phil,nice job! Stevens,way to go!
菲尔，干得好 史蒂芬，漂亮

323
00:21:10,78 --> 00:21:13,01
Goldberg,you maniac!
戈博，你这个疯子

324
00:21:13,25 --> 00:21:14,81
I love you!
我爱你

325
00:21:18,12 --> 00:21:20,92
-Couldn't have done it without you. -Thank you,sir.
宾，没有你可不行 谢谢

326
00:21:21,12 --> 00:21:22,42
Oh,excuse me.
抱歉

327
00:21:22,63 --> 00:21:26,36
I forgot my briefcase,you know, by accident.
我忘了拿公事包，不小心的

328
00:21:26,63 --> 00:21:30,16
Of course,you did. Forgot something else too,you bastard!
当然是不小心的 你还忘了一件事

329
00:21:32,84 --> 00:21:34,93
Well,what about you?
你呢？

330
00:21:35,17 --> 00:21:37,66
You're not feeling left out,are you?
不会觉得被冷落了吧？

331
00:21:38,98 --> 00:21:41,64
No,not at all. That's ridiculous.
一点也不会，开什么玩笑

332
00:21:41,85 --> 00:21:45,04
Everybody else got one, and you want one too. Don't you?
大家都有 你也想来一下，对吧？

333
00:21:48,39 --> 00:21:49,68
Yes,I do.
没错

334
00:21:49,99 --> 00:21:52,11
Now,get on out of here,you!
给我滚吧

335
00:21:57,39 --> 00:21:59,12
Pete Becker circles the ring.
彼特贝克绕着格斗场

336
00:21:59,36 --> 00:22:01,83
Looks like he's just trying to feel him out.
似乎想弄清楚自己的情势

337
00:22:02,03 --> 00:22:03,56
Bruiser is charging!
“重伤害”进攻了

338
00:22:03,83 --> 00:22:06,46
Run,you crazy,rich freak!
快逃啊，死有钱人

339
00:22:08,14 --> 00:22:09,40
I can't watch this.
我不敢看

340
00:22:09,67 --> 00:22:11,30
Check it out! Pete's winning!
你看，彼特要赢了

341
00:22:11,54 --> 00:22:12,67
Really?
真的？

342
00:22:16,08 --> 00:22:20,52
Bruiser has Becker on the canvas and is going for his favorite area!
“重伤害”把贝克打倒在地 向他最喜欢的部位进攻

343
00:22:22,32 --> 00:22:26,22
Wait! If that's his favorite area, why is he being so mean to it?
既然是最喜欢的部位 为何要下这种毒手？

344
00:22:26,89 --> 00:22:28,15
This is ironic.
真是讽刺

345
00:22:28,39 --> 00:22:31,05
Your last boyfriend,Richard, didn't want to have kids.
你的前任男友李察不想生小孩

346
00:22:31,33 --> 00:22:33,99
And from the looks of it, now Pete can't.
现在看情况，彼特是不能生

347
00:00:00,00 --> 00:00:00,00


348
